OL,3,CTata Steel: Unions vow to 'fight for
OL,4,CPort Talbot' as they take their
OL,5,Cprotests to Westminster
OL,7,FUnions have taken their battle for the
OL,8,Ffuture of Port Talbot to the heart of
OL,9,FWestminster, with a vocal
OL,10,Fdemonstration vowing to fight for the
OL,11,Ftown.
OL,13,FThe Unite union has called for the UK
OL,14,FGovernment to "up their investment" in
OL,15,Fthe Tata Steelworks to keep open the
OL,16,Ftwo blast furnaces whilst a new
OL,17,Felectric arc furnace is built.
