OL,7,FDavid TC Davies, the Welsh Secretary,
OL,8,Ftold ITV's Sharp End, "it with either
OL,9,Fa case of close the blast furnaces and
OL,10,Fleave or close the blast furnaces and
OL,11,Fbuild an arc furnace. There is no plan
OL,12,FC".
OL,14,FIf Tata Steel thought their
OL,15,Fannouncement on Friday, 19 January,
OL,16,Fwas the end of turbulence in Port
OL,17,FTalbot, they were wrong.
