OL,3,CTata Steel: Unions vow to 'fight for
OL,4,CPort Talbot' as they take their
OL,5,Cprotests to Westminster
OL,7,FThey took their protest to Westminster
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, 23 January, demanding the
OL,9,FUK Government invest more in the plant
OL,10,Fto save jobs.
OL,12,FUnite's Welsh general secretary said
OL,13,Fhe thought the #500 million doesn't
OL,14,Fcome close to matching investment in
OL,15,Fother countries.
OL,17,FPeter Hughes said, "Countries in the
OL,18,FG7 and G20 are actually giving a lot
OL,19,Fmore to their industries than the UK
OL,20,FGovernment are.
