OL,3,CTata Steel: Unions vow to 'fight for
OL,4,CPort Talbot' as they take their
OL,5,Cprotests to Westminster
OL,7,F"#500 million for two and a half
OL,8,Fredundancies is ridiculous. We do need
OL,9,Fan electric arc furnace, we do need to
OL,10,Fmove that forward, but there can be no
OL,11,Freason why that can't be run alongside
OL,12,Fthe blast furnaces already there", he
OL,13,Fcontinued.
OL,15,FIn November a multi-union plan,
OL,16,Fdevised by the Unite, Community and
OL,17,FGMB unions, was released to save more
OL,18,Fthan 2,300 jobs at Tata.
