OL,3,CTata Steel: Unions vow to 'fight for
OL,4,CPort Talbot' as they take their
OL,5,Cprotests to Westminster
OL,7,FThe plan would have seen the two
OL,8,Fexisting blast furnaces stay open,
OL,9,Fwhilst a new electric arc furnace is
OL,10,Fbuilt.
OL,12,FMr Hughes says more investment from
OL,13,Fthe UK Government means the blast
OL,14,Ffurnaces could stay open. "More money
OL,15,Fwould let you do the infrastructure
OL,16,Fright, you'd be able to run the
OL,17,Felectric arc furnace and the blast
OL,18,Ffurnace and making sure that we have a
OL,19,Ffuture.
