OL,5,Cprotests to Westminster
OL,7,FDavid TC Davies insisted that Tata
OL,8,Fwould not receive the investment from
OL,9,Fthe UK Government until they have
OL,10,Fbuilt the electric arc furnace in Port
OL,11,FTalbot.
OL,13,FTata Steel says it is committed to
OL,14,Fbuilding the new furnace. It has
OL,15,Fpledged a further #130 million to
OL,16,Fsupport workers to protect the futures
OL,17,Fof steelworkers in Port Talbot.
